column2: BRAVO BLACK TO PAPA BEAR. WE HAVE CLEARED THE ROAD BLOCK. ITS NOW UNDER OUR CONTROL. OUT.
BRAVO TO PAPA BEAR. LOOKS LIKE THATS THE LAST OF THEIR REINFORCEMENTS. WERE DONE HERE. OUT.
PAPA BEAR TO BRAVO BLACK. UNDERSTOOD, STAY ALERT FOR POSSIBLE REINFORCEMENTS. PAPA BEAR OUT.
PAPA BEAR TO BRAVO. ROGER THAT. MISSION ACCOMPLISHED. OUT.
